              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Neutron detector was gated to temporary count",
                "store for 40 mu-sec by coincident signals from neutron",
                "and fission counters. After waiting 100 mu-sec, back-",
                "ground was counted for 40 mu-sec. If a second fission",
                "had not occurred in the 180-sec counting cycle,",
                "contents of temporary store were transferred to the",
                "multiple event counter."
              ]
            }
          ],
