              "free_text": [
                "       For neutrons, 240 l. of Gadolinium-loaded",
                "trimethylbenzene scintillator (NE323) in a tank viewed",
                "by 12 EMI-9618A photomultipliers arranged in 3 coinci-",
                "dent banks of 4."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
