              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Linear fit of data was poor. Best two-line fit (minimum",
                "composite chi-squared)gives for neutron energy E in MeV",
                "  Nubar(E) = 2.491 + 0.035E for E less    than 0.44 MeV",
                "  Nubar(E) = 2.453 + 0.122E for E greater than 0.44 MeV",
                "These lines intersect at 440 keV. The thermal value",
                " (=2.491+-0.008) of Boldeman+Dalton (AAEC/E-172,3/67,",
                "see entry 30046.) has been included in the analysis.",
                "Similar analyses for U-235 and Pu-239 are discussed",
                "relative to the double-humped fission barrier in",
                "J.Nucl.En.25,321(1971)."
              ]
            }
